Changes always refer to the previous version.

JHelpDev 0.27

-James Iry added automatic TOC generation that merges with existing TOC items
 while keeping the current TOC structure intact
-no yellow (no target) highlighting for directories 
-some minor refactorings
-James Iry added environment settings to hold recently opened files and
the last directory the user looked in
-James Iry did some refactoring to move common XML parsing code into a 
 common base class
-Xml export via xmlenc
-removed XML libraries from distribution
-encodings not editable anymore, choose from all encodings supported by xmlenc